Package: rdatahub
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to Multiple Data Hub APIs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ernest", "Guevarra", email = "ernestgmd@gmail.com"", role = c("aut", "cre")) 
Description: The use of APIs to programmatically access data from repositories 
    allows efficient utilisation and facilitates subsequent analysis. rdatahub
    integrates the APIs of various open source data repositories into a single
    interface in R to support cross-platform data integration.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
